3
00:01:30,070 --> 00:01:31,900
Admiral Kizaru has made landfall!

4
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,660
The enemy has mobilized!

5
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:37,330
Don't let them fire those lasers!

6
00:01:37,330 --> 00:01:38,160
Attack!

7
00:01:59,850 --> 00:02:03,690
– It's a weaponized sea beast!
– It's a weaponized sea beast!

8
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:29,000
The weaponized sea beasts are attacking!

9
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,130
We're in trouble!

10
00:02:30,130 --> 00:02:33,590
We've gotta take them down
before they sink us!

11
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:46,650
Leave it to me!

12
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:51,610
Steam Knuckle!

13
00:03:09,090 --> 00:03:10,840
Forget the ships!

14
00:03:13,210 --> 00:03:15,510
You're dealing with me!

15
00:03:18,050 --> 00:03:20,260
The vice admirals have landed, too!

16
00:03:29,060 --> 00:03:32,190
Which lab are they holding
the Cipher Pol agents in?!

17
00:03:32,190 --> 00:03:33,440
The one up there.

18
00:03:41,370 --> 00:03:43,450
The Marines and the robot sea beasts...

19
00:03:43,450 --> 00:03:45,830
just started fighting at the shore!

20
00:03:46,210 --> 00:03:50,670
As long as Sentomaru
is commanding the pacifista,

21
00:03:50,670 --> 00:03:53,050
the island's defenses are impenetrable!

22
00:03:53,460 --> 00:03:57,630
Isn't that why he showed up?!
To take out Sentomaru?!

23
00:03:58,220 --> 00:03:59,340
Kizaru?!

24
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:01,100
He's here already?!

25
00:04:01,100 --> 00:04:03,010
No way!

26
00:04:03,010 --> 00:04:05,640
He's fighting right below us as we speak!

27
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:07,270
Kizaru, huh?

28
00:04:07,270 --> 00:04:11,110
This brings back some unpleasant
memories from Sabaody Archipelago...

29
00:04:18,530 --> 00:04:21,280
Too bad. You guys are toast.

30
00:04:21,280 --> 00:04:24,580
No way! Fighting Kizaru, of all people...

31
00:04:24,580 --> 00:04:26,450
I'm sorry, Sentomaru!

32
00:04:26,450 --> 00:04:28,710
What a heartbreaking battle!

33
00:04:28,710 --> 00:04:30,580
If you want to run, I understand!

34
00:04:30,580 --> 00:04:32,790
Keep your chin up, Stella!

35
00:04:32,790 --> 00:04:36,170
For now, just focus on cracking the passcode!

36
00:04:36,170 --> 00:04:38,090
Edison is right!

37
00:04:38,090 --> 00:04:39,090
We have to hurry!

38
00:04:40,510 --> 00:04:41,390
Okay!

39
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,600
Just surrender!

40
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:51,350
Sentomaru!

41
00:05:00,490 --> 00:05:03,370
Sacred Yasakani Jewel.

42
00:05:12,380 --> 00:05:13,710
I'm sorry, Unc!

43
00:05:14,210 --> 00:05:18,170
Straw Hat Luffy and I made a promise!

44
00:05:18,550 --> 00:05:20,420
Straw Hat?

45
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:23,140
Since when do you side with pirates?

46
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,650
I'll work with anyone...

47
00:05:37,690 --> 00:05:40,990
who helps the man that saved
my life escape this island!

48
00:06:07,850 --> 00:06:09,770
How odd.

49
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:13,520
They asked us to hunt bears, but...

50
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:15,440
Did that child beat us to it?

51
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:21,240
I hate the weaklings that live in the village!

52
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:23,450
I'm never going back!

53
00:06:23,450 --> 00:06:26,070
They kicked you out, huh?

54
00:06:27,490 --> 00:06:30,870
I'm so tough, I don't even get hungry!

55
00:06:30,870 --> 00:06:32,410
But I wanna work!

56
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:34,170
I want money!

57
00:06:34,170 --> 00:06:37,460
Oh, you have something you'd like to buy?

58
00:06:38,340 --> 00:06:39,500
Rice balls!

59
00:06:51,350 --> 00:06:54,230
You were such a cute kid...

60
00:06:54,940 --> 00:06:56,440
Work?

61
00:06:56,980 --> 00:07:00,190
You seem pretty confident
in your physical strength.

62
00:07:00,570 --> 00:07:03,780
Say, kid, how would you
like to be my bodyguard?

63
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:05,950
Are you gonna hire me?!

64
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:06,780
I'll do it!

65
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:16,750
Unc! Unc!

66
00:07:18,330 --> 00:07:19,340
You mean me?

67
00:07:19,340 --> 00:07:20,840
Unc!

68
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:23,920
How should I protect Old Man Punk?

69
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:26,380
Unc?

70
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:28,640
Do I look old enough to be an uncle?

71
00:07:28,890 --> 00:07:32,060
I want you to teach me, Unc!

72
00:07:35,770 --> 00:07:40,110
I did my best to teach you, Sentomaru.

73
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:43,530
Ashigara Dokkoi!

74
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:47,700
But...

75
00:07:49,780 --> 00:07:52,120
my defense...

76
00:07:55,370 --> 00:07:56,830
is as strong as yours.

77
00:08:24,030 --> 00:08:26,150
Pacifista.

78
00:08:29,990 --> 00:08:35,080
Your commander is unconscious,
so there will be a change of plans.

79
00:08:35,620 --> 00:08:41,080
Assist the Marine ships against
the weaponized sea beasts.

80
00:09:07,740 --> 00:09:09,450
The pacifista's directive...

81
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,530
has been overwritten.

82
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:14,700
Such a waste to sink them,

83
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:17,830
but if we can keep only one,
we choose the pacifista.

84
00:09:17,830 --> 00:09:20,290
Give me a full damage report...

85
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,460
of the last few minutes.

86
00:09:22,460 --> 00:09:23,170
Yes, sir!

87
00:09:26,130 --> 00:09:28,460
Sentomaru is down!

88
00:09:29,090 --> 00:09:29,920
What?!

89
00:09:38,770 --> 00:09:41,520
Let's hurry and deactivate the defense system!

90
00:09:41,890 --> 00:09:42,770
Yeah!

91
00:09:43,310 --> 00:09:47,320
We can't let Sentomaru's sacrifice be in vain!

92
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:51,400
Forget it. I'm Vegapunk, too!

93
00:09:55,450 --> 00:09:57,660
Kizaru is light itself!

94
00:09:57,660 --> 00:10:00,000
He can pass through the laser barrier!

95
00:10:03,830 --> 00:10:05,840
What?!

96
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:08,210
You mean he can just come right in?!

97
00:10:08,710 --> 00:10:09,670
Yes!

98
00:10:13,130 --> 00:10:17,680
He totally wiped the floor
with us once already!

99
00:10:20,350 --> 00:10:23,270
It's been a while...

100
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:26,150
Straw Hat crew.

101
00:10:43,330 --> 00:10:44,870
Hurry up, hurry up!

102
00:10:45,370 --> 00:10:47,790
As soon as the barrier
is down, we're outta here!

103
00:10:48,250 --> 00:10:50,500
So far, so good!

104
00:10:51,300 --> 00:10:53,800
I'll just take the ship around back!

105
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:54,970
Sounds good!

106
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:03,140
Let's eat while we can.

107
00:11:05,390 --> 00:11:06,270
Yeah.

108
00:11:09,650 --> 00:11:11,980
You can't fight on an empty stomach.

109
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:14,570
You're eating now, of all times?

110
00:11:14,570 --> 00:11:17,780
We're gonna escape soon, guys!

111
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:25,410
Lilith! What's up with that?!

112
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:28,040
An emergency alarm?!

113
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:30,750
Why?! I thought this place...

114
00:11:30,750 --> 00:11:33,090
was impenetrable!

115
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:49,020
At any cost, protect:

116
00:11:49,770 --> 00:11:51,980
The power plant.

117
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:55,440
Punk Records.

118
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,910
York.

119
00:11:58,910 --> 00:12:00,410
And ideally...

120
00:12:00,410 --> 00:12:01,870
an old friend...

121
00:12:02,490 --> 00:12:05,120
but alas...

122
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:09,670
At any cost, eliminate:

123
00:12:10,830 --> 00:12:14,800
Dr. Vegapunk.

124
00:12:15,130 --> 00:12:18,590
Kizaru made it inside the dome!

125
00:12:20,220 --> 00:12:22,600
Luffy and the others are out there!

126
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:25,100
That can't be good. Luffy!

127
00:12:25,100 --> 00:12:27,350
Tell them through the snail!

128
00:12:27,350 --> 00:12:29,650
Luffy! Run!

129
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:34,980
Until the ship is in place,

130
00:12:34,980 --> 00:12:36,610
I won't deactivate the barrier!

131
00:13:07,270 --> 00:13:08,810
Stussy!

132
00:13:09,770 --> 00:13:11,480
Stussy?!

133
00:13:12,060 --> 00:13:13,480
Nami, I'm borrowing this!

134
00:13:13,060 --> 00:13:13,480
What?

135
00:13:16,190 --> 00:13:17,690
Sheesh! What gives?!

136
00:13:17,690 --> 00:13:19,240
A bubble gun?!

137
00:13:19,490 --> 00:13:21,860
Looks like he forgot about you!

138
00:13:21,860 --> 00:13:23,320
Huh?!

139
00:13:33,420 --> 00:13:36,250
So you got backup and thought
you could make your move?!

140
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:38,710
Between Kizaru and me,

141
00:13:39,090 --> 00:13:41,180
all of you are dead!

142
00:13:41,180 --> 00:13:43,510
Don't underestimate us!

143
00:14:08,450 --> 00:14:11,660
No wonder their ship wasn't at the shore.

144
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:14,540
It was here all along!

145
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:16,210
Hurry up!

146
00:14:17,920 --> 00:14:20,670
Kizaru?! He's a Marine admiral!

147
00:14:20,670 --> 00:14:21,970
What's the plan, Luffy?!

148
00:14:23,340 --> 00:14:25,220
Where'd he go?!

149
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:27,350
Hey, Luffy!

150
00:14:39,730 --> 00:14:41,320
Hey, long time no–

151
00:14:51,040 --> 00:14:54,370
That's just bad manners.

152
00:14:55,330 --> 00:14:56,880
Kizaru!

153
00:14:56,880 --> 00:14:59,170
Compared to two years ago...

154
00:14:59,800 --> 00:15:02,090
we're a hundred times stronger!

155
00:15:19,150 --> 00:15:20,980
He's finally reached the top!

156
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:23,940
Invincible Slave Kuma has returned!

157
00:15:27,910 --> 00:15:32,120
Soldiers, stop him!

158
00:15:38,210 --> 00:15:40,920
What's he doing here?!

159
00:15:47,680 --> 00:15:48,550
Oh no!

160
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:50,350
We can't stop him!

161
00:16:06,110 --> 00:16:07,860
Ursus Shock!

162
00:16:26,340 --> 00:16:28,470
Such an insolent slave...

163
00:16:40,520 --> 00:16:42,480
What do you think you're doing?

164
00:16:44,110 --> 00:16:47,440
The other day it was the
Revolutionary Army, and now this...

165
00:16:50,950 --> 00:16:54,540
This destruction is unprecedented, Kuma!

166
00:16:58,250 --> 00:17:00,750
F-Fleet Admiral Sakazuki...

167
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:05,170
Worthless scum!

168
00:17:05,460 --> 00:17:08,670
You soldiers are completely useless!

169
00:17:08,670 --> 00:17:10,680
Hey, Akainu!

170
00:17:11,390 --> 00:17:15,760
I ordered lobster for dinner last night,
but they said they were all out!

171
00:17:15,760 --> 00:17:17,930
That's never happened before!

172
00:17:17,930 --> 00:17:20,640
What's happening to
Mary Geoise's food supply?!

173
00:17:21,230 --> 00:17:23,610
Hey, that's not important right now!

174
00:17:23,610 --> 00:17:25,860
I've just been injured!

175
00:17:26,280 --> 00:17:29,490
Kuma the Tyrant is a mere slave!

176
00:17:29,490 --> 00:17:31,570
Execute him already!

177
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:35,280
The thing is, Kuma...

178
00:17:35,280 --> 00:17:37,790
if we can't control you,

179
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:43,250
then we can't afford to have you on the loose.

180
00:17:43,250 --> 00:17:46,380
Your sense of self should have been erased.

181
00:17:47,460 --> 00:17:50,130
You're as good as dead already.

182
00:17:52,180 --> 00:17:54,680
So where do you think you're going?!

183
00:18:04,980 --> 00:18:06,730
Hellhound!

184
00:18:10,690 --> 00:18:13,860
I didn't know you still bled like a man.

185
00:18:24,370 --> 00:18:25,500
Hold it, Kuma!

186
00:18:58,620 --> 00:19:02,790
Bark all you want, but Kuma
will never regain his sense of self.

187
00:19:02,790 --> 00:19:07,460
He volunteered to be reborn as a weapon.

188
00:19:07,460 --> 00:19:08,590
That's a lie!

189
00:19:10,880 --> 00:19:12,590
There's no way...

190
00:19:12,590 --> 00:19:14,930
There's no way he chose that!

191
00:19:15,260 --> 00:19:19,220
He would never leave me behind!

192
00:19:24,100 --> 00:19:27,020
Hey! Where is Kuma?!

193
00:19:27,020 --> 00:19:29,270
Don't tell me you let him get away!

194
00:19:29,860 --> 00:19:32,400
You're the fleet admiral!

195
00:19:34,780 --> 00:19:36,780
Where are you going?

196
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:39,780
You're just a puppet...

197
00:19:40,490 --> 00:19:43,750
without a mind or free will...

198
00:19:47,330 --> 00:19:51,170
Pacifista and all Marines, keep shooting!

199
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:54,720
Destroy the weaponized sea beasts!

200
00:20:06,940 --> 00:20:10,520
Enter the Fabriophase! Occupy the island!

201
00:20:11,190 --> 00:20:14,440
Admiral Kizaru has entered
the Labophase above the clouds!

202
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:38,220
Gum-Gum...

203
00:20:41,510 --> 00:20:43,600
Black Mamba!

204
00:20:49,230 --> 00:20:52,980
Now I see how you were able to defeat Kaido.

205
00:20:52,980 --> 00:20:54,780
You're quite the powerhouse.

206
00:20:54,780 --> 00:20:55,900
However...

207
00:20:58,110 --> 00:21:03,620
what would make a pirate like you
want to protect Vegapunk?

208
00:21:04,990 --> 00:21:07,450
You tell me!

209
00:21:07,450 --> 00:21:11,460
Why do you guys wanna kill Apple Gramps?!

210
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:20,380
It's not that I want to...

211
00:21:29,770 --> 00:21:32,150
How far is he going?!

212
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:43,490
I don't want to kill him.

213
00:21:47,450 --> 00:21:50,580
I've known Vegapunk for a long time...

214
00:21:51,790 --> 00:21:55,790
so I'd appreciate it if you'd stay out of this.

215
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:03,510
Acceleration is power!

216
00:22:18,150 --> 00:22:19,940
It's complete!

217
00:22:20,740 --> 00:22:23,910
Its name is Vegaforce-01!

218
00:22:24,280 --> 00:22:26,910
The dream of man!

219
00:22:29,870 --> 00:22:31,790
A giant robot!

220
00:22:45,390 --> 00:22:47,850
Luffy!

221
00:22:48,140 --> 00:22:50,600
What's going on?!

222
00:23:11,410 --> 00:23:13,460
I thought I was a goner!

223
00:23:18,170 --> 00:23:19,790
Oh... Oh no!

224
00:23:21,130 --> 00:23:24,930
Franky! Bonney!

225
00:23:24,930 --> 00:23:26,090
Huh?

226
00:23:26,090 --> 00:23:27,340
Lilith?!

227
00:23:28,510 --> 00:23:30,680
Run!

228
00:23:30,680 --> 00:23:32,600
The Vegaforce-01 is gonna...

229
00:23:33,100 --> 00:23:35,230
Just run!

230
00:23:58,880 --> 00:24:01,170
Damn it all!

231
00:24:01,170 --> 00:24:05,800
The robot of our dreams, the Vegaforce-01...

232
00:24:06,300 --> 00:24:09,050
That jackass is gonna pay!

233
00:24:10,390 --> 00:24:11,550
Is the Sunny alright?!

234
00:24:13,430 --> 00:24:16,520
Hey! Straw Hat flew right through us!

235
00:24:25,530 --> 00:24:28,700
Kizaru, you bastard!

236
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:37,370
Look how big you've gotten, Bonney...

237
00:24:37,370 --> 00:24:40,630
Kids these days grow up so fast.

238
00:24:43,590 --> 00:24:45,710
Are you still carrying a grudge?

239
00:24:45,710 --> 00:24:51,180
An order was issued to assassinate
the man you hate, Dr. Vegapunk.

240
00:24:53,890 --> 00:24:54,890
Shut up.

241
00:24:55,850 --> 00:24:59,100
I have a new target in my crosshairs!

242
00:25:03,730 --> 00:25:05,190
Age Skewer!

243
00:25:05,940 --> 00:25:06,690
Whoa.

244
00:25:11,700 --> 00:25:13,870
I'd prefer...

245
00:25:14,910 --> 00:25:18,790
not to hurt any acquaintances
outside the scope of my mission.

246
00:25:22,830 --> 00:25:24,500
No! Not that way...!

247
00:25:24,500 --> 00:25:26,590
Bonney!

248
00:25:32,340 --> 00:25:36,180
That's it, Kizaru!

249
00:25:36,180 --> 00:25:39,350
Radical...

250
00:25:40,810 --> 00:25:43,310
Be–

251
00:25:44,440 --> 00:25:45,770
Huh?!

252
00:25:45,770 --> 00:25:46,940
Where'd he go?!

253
00:25:46,940 --> 00:25:48,230
He just vanished?!

254
00:25:50,150 --> 00:25:51,490
Stella's in danger!

255
00:25:51,490 --> 00:25:53,360
Franky! Call them!

256
00:25:53,360 --> 00:25:54,070
Huh?

257
00:25:59,870 --> 00:26:01,540
Come in, control room!

258
00:26:01,540 --> 00:26:03,250
Franky, are you okay?!

259
00:26:03,250 --> 00:26:05,250
We heard a big explosion over there!

260
00:26:05,250 --> 00:26:08,050
That you, Usopp? Is everyone alright?!

261
00:26:08,050 --> 00:26:10,380
What? Y-Yeah...

262
00:26:10,380 --> 00:26:13,890
Good to hear! So he's not there yet.

263
00:26:13,890 --> 00:26:15,600
What do you mean?

264
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:17,720
Eureka!

265
00:26:17,720 --> 00:26:20,430
The deactivation code
for the defense system...

266
00:26:22,810 --> 00:26:25,190
– ...is cracked!
– ...is cracked!

267
00:26:25,690 --> 00:26:26,650
Really?!

268
00:26:29,440 --> 00:26:31,280
In your face, York!

269
00:26:31,280 --> 00:26:32,490
For real?!

270
00:26:32,490 --> 00:26:35,620
Dammit! You smart-asses!

271
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:39,830
Franky, we can bring down
the barrier at any time!

272
00:26:39,830 --> 00:26:43,040
Did you move the Vegaforce-01
and the ship to the back?!

273
00:26:43,040 --> 00:26:44,710
No, because...

274
00:26:47,750 --> 00:26:50,130
What a pity.

275
00:26:50,460 --> 00:26:53,010
Your escape plan has failed.

276
00:26:56,430 --> 00:26:58,140
Vegapunk.

277
